title: Kadamban
subTitle: Kadamban lives a peaceful life with the villagers in a remote forest in Tamil Nadu. Things take a turn when a business tycoon decides to drive his tribe out of the area in order to extract minerals.

title: Hunterrr
subTitle: Mandar is a self-confessed sex addict who is only interested in sex and holds no regards for love or feelings. However, his life changes when he meets Tripti and wishes to settle down with her.

title: Krishna Ka Badla
subTitle: A disillusioned actor, Babu, reluctantly joins a drama troupe for one last play. He teams up with journalist Meera and together they uncover a dangerous conspiracy that treatens them both.

title: Aakhri Chaal : Ab kaun bachega
subTitle: Three brothers conspire against each other in a bid to take over their father's criminal empire following his sudden death. Meanwhile, someone else tries to take advantage of the rift between them.

title: Road to Sangam
subTitle: A devout Muslim Indian man is tasked with repairing a lorry in order to transport the ashes of Mahatma Gandhi. However, when communal violence strikes, he is left with a troubling dilemma.

title: Return of Hanuman
subTitle: Lord Hanuman reincarnates as Maruti to help Minku, a bullied boy, while addressing challenges of modern life, courage and the importance of protecting nature.

title: Meri Jaan
subTitle: A young man faces challenges and attempts to recover his debts. However, in the process, he also realises that he is in love with someone.

title: Fidaa
subTitle: An NRI medical student falls in love with a vivacious woman. However, they face challenges in their relationship due to their differences in personalities.

title: Mardaani 2
subTitle: A twenty-one-year-old psychopath has an affinity towards raping and murdering young woman. But, a cop, Shivani Shivaji Roy, is on his heels as she tries to bring him to justice.

title: Hidimbha
subTitle: In Hyderabad, a series of murders targets young girls. Later, officers Aadhya and Abhay investigate as more victims disappear, soon discovering a common link among them.

title: Etharkkum Thunindhavan
subTitle: Kannabiran, a lawyer, saves a young woman from a pornography racket run by Inba, a minister's son. However, Inba threatens to leak explicit videos of several women, making Kannabiran go after him.

title: Subham
subTitle: When a soap opera mysteriously enchants the town's female residents, their husbands embark on a quest to uncover the truth.

title: Subham
subTitle: When a soap opera mysteriously enchants the town's female residents, their husbands embark on a quest to uncover the truth.

title: Parking
subTitle: A parking spot frays the relationship between two neighbours of different generations and world views. Soon, the two men find themselves in an escalating battle to have the space all to themselves.

title: Jaane Bhi Do Yaaro
subTitle: Two photographers, who are employed by a newspaper editor to expose the scandalous activities of the rich, come across corruption by a builder and accidentally photograph a murder.

title: Zed Plus
subTitle: Aslam, a villager who runs a small business, accidentally meets the prime minister of India, who grants him special security on his request. Soon, he starts chasing political ambitions.

title: Baazaar
subTitle: An amateur stock trader, Rizwan, goes to Mumbai and works for the successful Gujarati trader, Shakun Kothari. Everything seems to be going smooth until Rizwan faces betrayal from his idol.

title: Bharaate
subTitle: Jagan, a local travel guide, falls in love with Radha, a tourist who visits his city. Though she leaves without saying goodbye, fate conspires to being them together again.

title: Guru
subTitle: A failed boxer sees potential in a vegetable seller and begins training her in boxing. However, the two don't get along due to the former's harsh training style.

title: Housefull 2
subTitle: Four men join hands to date and marry the women of their dreams by changing their identities and deceiving their prospective fathers-in-law.

title: DD Returns
subTitle: An event manager and his friends hide the money they stole in a haunted bungalow to evade the police but when they go back to retrieve it, the ghosts force them to play a dangerous game.

title: Buddy
subTitle: A terrible accident leaves Pallavi in a coma while her soul possesses the body of a teddy bear. With her organs in danger of being traded, she enlists the help of a pilot, Aditya.

title: Tiger Nageswara Rao
subTitle: In the 1970s, a daring thief named Tiger Nageswara Rao becomes a legend due to the heists he masterminds and the ingenious ways by which he evades the police.

title: Bogan
subTitle: A police officer probes a seasoned robber, oblivious to his hidden power, which allows him to possess people through eye contact.

title: Bogan
subTitle: A police officer probes a seasoned robber, oblivious to his hidden power, which allows him to possess people through eye contact.

title: Kabzaa - The Mafia Raaj
subTitle: Vijay Chandra, a determined police aspirant, battles a local MLA's corrupt efforts to seize his family's land. Joined by other wronged citizens, he takes a stand for justice and honor.

title: ABHIMANYU
subTitle: Arjun seeks to change the education system by putting his life at risk to nationalise private schools in the country. Will he succeed in his efforts?

title: Fool N Final
subTitle: A heist to find a precious diamond goes hilariously wrong when the group of thieves decide to escape the clutches of their leader.

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jehadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.

title: Rowdy Baadshah
subTitle: A man fails to get a job with the police force due to his father's connections with a gangster. However, when his brother is killed by the latter, he sets out on the path of revenge.

title: Vivegam
subTitle: Ajay Kumar, a former counter-terrorism agent, is called for a special mission. However, he is betrayed by his friends and is accused of extremely treasonous acts.

title: Kabali
subTitle: A man spends 25 years in prison for fighting against oppression. Old but still bloodthirsty, he decides to seek revenge against his enemies upon his release.

title: Kaala Karikalan
subTitle: Haridev Abhayankar, a corrupt minister, wishes to seize Dharavi's lucrative land for his own gain. However, Karikaalan, the locality's godfather, fights to protect his people's rights and assets.

title: Bhagavanth Kesari
subTitle: A former prisoner is adamant about training his adoptive daughter to join the Indian Army. However, his mission is interrupted by a conflict with a ruthless businessman.

title: Kaduva
subTitle: Kaduva pledges to seek revenge against IG Joseph when the police officer sends Kaduva to jail and torments his loved ones.
